{
  "title": "Changing mortality and average cohort life expectancy",
  "abstract": "Period life expectancy varies with changes in mortality, and should not be confused with the life expectancy of those alive during that period. Given past and likely future mortality changes, a recent debate has arisen on the usefulness of the period",
